355 '----------- MAIN STRATEGY LOOP ------------
356 '
360 FOR I = 10 TO 100 STEP 2
370    GOSUB 600'PICK UP PLAYER INPUT
380    T = T - P: LOCATE I + 1, 40: PRINT T;
